p-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_teaser.jpg 2000w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_teaser-297x163.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_teaser-800x440.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_teaser-120x66.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_teaser-768x422.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_teaser-1536x845.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_teaser-696x383.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_teaser-1068x587.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_teaser-1920x1056.jpg 1920w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_teaser-764x420.jpg 764w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-251202\">c. Mondraker</figcaption></figure><p>Mondraker Mind is not the first suspension telemetry system we’ve seen, even outside of the pro racing circuits. But it’s certainly the first to be so neatly integrated into a complete bike by the original manufacturer – <em>with the aim of making data logging simpler &amp; more accessible.</em></p><p>While other comprehensive <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2020/09/24/byb-telemetry-is-back-with-smarter-v2-0-of-accessible-pro-level-suspension-analysis-tool/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">telemetry setups</a> require oftentimes bulky &amp; complex installations adapted to work on each bike, Mondraker’s Mind is so neatly integrated that you’ll forget it is there on your bike – constantly tracking how your bike moves, and automatically uploading its data to the cloud for you to analyze and plan how to tweak your setup.<span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-medrectangle-3\"></span></p><p><span><iframe width=\"696\" height=\"392\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation\" data-ezsrc=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/jUB-m0J3HCM?version=3&amp;rel=1&amp;showsearch=0&amp;showinfo=1&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;fs=1&amp;hl=en-US&amp;autohide=2&amp;wmode=transparent\"></iframe></span></p><p>Mondraker says it’s taken them more than three years to adapt their own pro-team World Cup racing tech into a user-friendly system that any rider can use to get “more speed and more flow”… “the world’s first fully-integrated telemetry device for mountain bikes”.</p><h3>What is suspension telemetry tracking?</h3><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_installation.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_installation.jpg\" alt=\"Mondraker MIND integrated telemetry tracking system suspension setup and analysis,&nbsp;rear angled teaser\" width=\"1600\" height=\"820\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_installation.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_installation.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_installation-297x152.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_installation-800x410.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_installation-120x62.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_installation-768x394.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_installation-1536x787.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_installation-696x357.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_installation-1068x547.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_installation-820x420.jpg 820w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_installation.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_installation-297x152.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_installation-800x410.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_installation-120x62.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_installation-768x394.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_installation-1536x787.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_installation-696x357.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_installation-1068x547.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_installation-820x420.jpg 820w\"></a></p><p>The basic idea behind Mondraker Mind (and other similar tools) is to measure every tiny movement of your suspension, log all of that data, and present it in a way to better understand how best to optimize setup. While it starts with perfectly dialing in sag guided by the companion app, Mind reaches much further into figuring out what settings give you the best balance of control, grip, comfort, and ultimately speed.</p><h3>Tech details – How does Mind work?</h3><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_fork-steerer-sensor.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_fork-steerer-sensor.jpg\" alt=\"Mondraker MIND integrated telemetry tracking system suspension setup and analysis,&nbsp;fork smart sensor\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_fork-steerer-sensor.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_fork-steerer-sensor.jpg 2000w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_fork-steerer-sensor-297x178.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_fork-steerer-sensor-800x480.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_fork-steerer-sensor-120x72.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_fork-steerer-sensor-768x461.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_fork-steerer-sensor-1536x922.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_fork-steerer-sensor-696x418.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_fork-steerer-sensor-1068x641.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_fork-steerer-sensor-1920x1152.jpg 1920w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_fork-steerer-sensor-700x420.jpg 700w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_fork-steerer-sensor.jpg 2000w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_fork-steerer-sensor-297x178.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_fork-steerer-sensor-800x480.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_fork-steerer-sensor-120x72.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_fork-steerer-sensor-768x461.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_fork-steerer-sensor-1536x922.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_fork-steerer-sensor-696x418.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_fork-steerer-sensor-1068x641.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_fork-steerer-sensor-1920x1152.jpg 1920w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_fork-steerer-sensor-700x420.jpg 700w\"></a></p><p>Mind works by linking two wireless sensor pairs, in the front and back. A data logger/sending unit inside the steerer and under the fork crown tracks fork movement via a sensor magnet on the left leg. In the rear, a smaller smart sensor sits on the rocker arm, tracking rear suspension movement via a tiny sensor magnet <em>on that main rocker pivot</em>. Together they log every bit of suspension movement “<em>millisecond by millisecond and millimetre by millimetre</em>” (<em>capturing data at a rate of 100Hz</em>), store it in local memory, then upload it to Mondraker’s online myMondraker platform when you sync via a smartphone app after the ride.</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_smart-sensor-details.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_smart-sensor-details.jpg\" alt=\"Mondraker MIND integrated telemetry tracking system suspension setup and analysis,&nbsp;front &amp; rear smart sensors\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_smart-sensor-details.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_smart-sensor-details.jpg 2000w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_smart-sensor-details-297x178.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_smart-sensor-details-800x480.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_smart-sensor-details-120x72.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_smart-sensor-details-768x461.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_smart-sensor-details-1536x922.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_smart-sensor-details-696x418.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_smart-sensor-details-1068x641.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_smart-sensor-details-1920x1152.jpg 1920w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_smart-sensor-details-700x420.jpg 700w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_smart-sensor-details.jpg 2000w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_smart-sensor-details-297x178.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_smart-sensor-details-800x480.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_smart-sensor-details-120x72.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_smart-sensor-details-768x461.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_smart-sensor-details-1536x922.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_smart-sensor-details-696x418.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_smart-sensor-details-1068x641.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_smart-sensor-details-1920x1152.jpg 1920w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-system-suspension-setup-and-analysis_smart-sensor-details-700x420.jpg 700w\"></a></p><p><span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-box-4\"></span>More than just shock movement, Mind also has onboard GPS tracking to compile suspension movement with real speed, distance, time &amp; elevation data out on the trail. You’ll even be able to pair your myMondraker account to automatically upload your rides to Strava, no extra device required. Use that data to figure out which lines are fastest, or which descents put the most demand on your suspension.</p><p>That also lets Mind track your air time, much like the latest <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2020/06/16/garmin-edge-1030-plus-130-plus-gps-cycling-computers-get-bigger-faster-feature-sets/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Garmin Edge</a> computers or even <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2018/08/28/first-look-fox-live-valve-tracks-any-terrain-with-automatic-damping-control/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Fox Live Valve</a>, which should make for some fun post-ride analysis sessions… and a new stat to compete with your riding buddies.</p><p>All of that telemetry data, suspension analysis &amp; post-ride graphics are visible on the smartphone app, or from any computer via your myMondraker.com account to get the best view of the data on a bigger screen.</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-suspension-setup-and-analysis_front-and-rear-sensor-setup.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-suspension-setup-and-analysis_front-and-rear-sensor-setup.jpg\" alt=\"Mondraker MIND integrated telemetry tracking system suspension setup and analysis,&nbsp;fork &amp; shock sensors\" width=\"1800\" height=\"1000\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-suspension-setup-and-analysis_front-and-rear-sensor-setup.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-suspension-setup-and-analysis_front-and-rear-sensor-setup.jpg 1800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-suspension-setup-and-analysis_front-and-rear-sensor-setup-297x165.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-suspension-setup-and-analysis_front-and-rear-sensor-setup-800x444.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-suspension-setup-and-analysis_front-and-rear-sensor-setup-120x67.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-suspension-setup-and-analysis_front-and-rear-sensor-setup-768x427.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-suspension-setup-and-analysis_front-and-rear-sensor-setup-1536x853.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-suspension-setup-and-analysis_front-and-rear-sensor-setup-696x387.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-suspension-setup-and-analysis_front-and-rear-sensor-setup-1068x593.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-suspension-setup-and-analysis_front-and-rear-sensor-setup-756x420.jpg 756w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-suspension-setup-and-analysis_front-and-rear-sensor-setup.jpg 1800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-suspension-setup-and-analysis_front-and-rear-sensor-setup-297x165.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-suspension-setup-and-analysis_front-and-rear-sensor-setup-800x444.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-suspension-setup-and-analysis_front-and-rear-sensor-setup-120x67.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-suspension-setup-and-analysis_front-and-rear-sensor-setup-768x427.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-suspension-setup-and-analysis_front-and-rear-sensor-setup-1536x853.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-suspension-setup-and-analysis_front-and-rear-sensor-setup-696x387.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-suspension-setup-and-analysis_front-and-rear-sensor-setup-1068x593.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-suspension-setup-and-analysis_front-and-rear-sensor-setup-756x420.jpg 756w\"></a></p><p>Both of the smart sensors are self-powered with USB-C rechargeable batteries (<em>charged on the bike in about 1hr</em>), a continuous ridetime of 20 hours between charges, or 15 days on standby. Combined, the four total sensors add just a claimed 199g to your bike.</p><p>Another bonus feature is anti-theft bike tracking (since each Mind system is unique, non-transferable, and linked to the bike’s serial number in production.) Mind is already tracking every movement of your bike on its own (<em>once you start &amp; stop data collection with your paired smartphone</em>), so Mondraker also included a built-in alarm system that can be activated for security and set to notify you if your bike moves unexpectedly, and then can track its location if someone does try to actually steal it.<span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-large-leaderboard-2\"></span></p><h3>Mondraker Mind – Availability, options &amp; future outlook</h3><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-suspension-setup-and-analysis_rear-end-smart-sensor.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-suspension-setup-and-analysis_rear-end-smart-sensor.jpg\" alt=\"Mondraker MIND integrated telemetry tracking system suspension setup and analysis,&nbsp;rear smart sensor\" width=\"1600\" height=\"900\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-suspension-setup-and-analysis_rear-end-smart-sensor.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-suspension-setup-and-analysis_rear-end-smart-sensor.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-suspension-setup-and-analysis_rear-end-smart-sensor-297x167.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-suspension-setup-and-analysis_rear-end-smart-sensor-800x450.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-suspension-setup-and-analysis_rear-end-smart-sensor-120x68.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-suspension-setup-and-analysis_rear-end-smart-sensor-768x432.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-suspension-setup-and-analysis_rear-end-smart-sensor-1536x864.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-suspension-setup-and-analysis_rear-end-smart-sensor-696x392.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-suspension-setup-and-analysis_rear-end-smart-sensor-1068x601.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-suspension-setup-and-analysis_rear-end-smart-sensor-747x420.jpg 747w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-suspension-setup-and-analysis_rear-end-smart-sensor.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-suspension-setup-and-analysis_rear-end-smart-sensor-297x167.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-suspension-setup-and-analysis_rear-end-smart-sensor-800x450.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-suspension-setup-and-analysis_rear-end-smart-sensor-120x68.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-suspension-setup-and-analysis_rear-end-smart-sensor-768x432.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-suspension-setup-and-analysis_rear-end-smart-sensor-1536x864.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-suspension-setup-and-analysis_rear-end-smart-sensor-696x392.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-suspension-setup-and-analysis_rear-end-smart-sensor-1068x601.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Mondraker-MIND-integrated-telemetry-tracking-suspension-setup-and-analysis_rear-end-smart-sensor-747x420.jpg 747w\"></a></p><p>The one real catch to Mind is that the system is specifically tailored to and neatly integrated into the bike, so it isn’t simply something that can be retrofitted. So for the time being, the only way to get it will be to buy a new top-shelf 2021 Mondraker Foxy Carbon enduro bike (models R, RR &amp; XR) or Crafty Carbon e-enduro eMTB (models R, RR, XR &amp; RR SL). And those aren’t bikes that will come cheap. (<em>It does appear that 2020 Foxy Carbon buyers may be able to upgrade their newly-bought bike through their dealer.</em>)</p><p>Mondraker’s top 2021 Foxy Carbon XR sells for around <em>9500€</em>, or make that <em>12,300€</em> for the top Crafty Carbon RR SL e-bike – <em>before you add MIND telemetry tracking.</em><span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-leader-1\"></span></p><h3><em>Mondraker MIND – Pricing &amp; availability</em></h3><figure id=\"attachment_251209\" aria-describedby=\"capti